Air Products Withdraws $5.9 Billion Airgas Offer After Losing Bid in Court

-- B y   Z a c h a r y   R .   M i d e r
-- 
2011-02-15T23:34:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-15/air-products-withdraws-5-9-billion-airgas-offer-after-losing-bid-in-court.html
     Feb. 15 (Bloomberg) -  Air Products & Chemicals Inc .
withdrew its $5.9 billion hostile offer for  Airgas Inc . after
losing a bid to invalidate a poison-pill defense.  Air Products announced the decision in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
